text: The 1992 Yukon general election was held on October 19, 1992 to elect members of the Legislative Assembly of the territory of Yukon, Canada. It was won by the Yukon Party. ==Results by party== Party Party Leader # of cands Seats Before After % of vote Yukon Party John Ostashek 14 7 7 35.9 NDP Tony Penikett 17 9 6 35.1 Independent 7 0 3
